26/07/2006
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Officials meeting on Tuesday (25 July) agreed that Macedonian and US soldiers would conduct a joint military exercise starting on 9 September at the Krivolak military ground near Skopje. The manoeuvres would be part of a co-operation initiative involving the exchange of small military units, which is being implemented by Macedonian military police and the Vermont National Guard. (Makfax - 25/07/06)
